  "readme_html": "\n        \n          <p><img src=\"https://github.com/jmorganca/ollama/assets/251292/700d0dcf-3bc0-406f-b289-e48965e8f602\" width=\"280\"/></p>\n\n<p>Codebooga was created by merging two existing models:</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://ollama.ai/library/phind-codellama\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phind-CodeLlama-34B-v2</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://ollama.ai/library/wizardcoder\" rel=\"nofollow\">WizardCoder-Python-34B-V1.0</a></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>It was created by using the <a href=\"https://github.com/Gryphe/BlockMerge_Gradient\" rel=\"nofollow\">BlockMerge Gradient</a> script.</p>\n\n<h3>Example prompts</h3>\n\n<pre><code>Write the javascript react code to render a sign up form\n</code></pre>\n\n<pre><code>Where is the bug in this code?\n\ndef fib(n):\n    if n &lt;= 0:\n        return n\n    else:\n        return fib(n-1) + fib(n-2)\n</code></pre>\n\n<h3>Recommended parameters</h3>\n\n<pre><code>temperature: 1.31\ntop_p: 0.14\nrepeat_penalty: 1.17\ntop_k: 49\n</code></pre>\n\n<h2>References</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/oobabooga/CodeBooga-34B-v0.1\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hugging Face</a></p>\n\n        \n      ",
